  code:'// Phantom reference pattern:\nReferenceQueue<MyObj> queue = new ReferenceQueue<>();\nPhantomReference<MyObj> ref = new PhantomReference<>(myObj, queue);\nmyObj = null; // release strong ref\n// ... later in cleanup thread:\nReference<?> cleared = queue.poll();\nif (cleared != null) {\n  // safe to release native resources\n  nativeCleanup(); \n}',
