    'VarHandle (Java 9+): like MethodHandle but for fields. Supports atomic operations: getAndSet, compareAndSet, getAcquire/setRelease for fine-grained memory ordering',
    'Performance: after JIT warmup, MethodHandle.invoke() has zero overhead over direct call. Method.invoke() always has overhead (array boxing of args, security checks)',
